metadata.description: DESTRO, one of COBRA's top operatives, has been captured. As the metal masked maverick gets transferred to a new prison, a prison break is instigated by none other than... SNAKE EYES!  With DESTRO free and SNAKE EYES under COBRA's control, a mission that will rock the world of G.I. JOE begins!
metadata.name: G.I. Joe: Snake Eyes, Agent of Cobra
